1. *Deset* puta sam ti rekao da neću da idem. (I told you ten times that I won't go.)
2. Imali smo *deset* minuta za odgovor. (We had ten minutes for the answer.) 
3. *Deset* ljudi je prisustvovalo sastanku. (Ten people attended the meeting.)
4. Onda je on brojao do *deset*. (Then he was counting to ten.)
5. *Deset* sekundi je dovoljno. (Ten seconds is enough.)
6. Pričali smo o *deset* minuta. (We talked for ten minutes.)
7. *Deset* septembra je bio rođendan moje sestre. (My sister's birthday was on the 10th of September.)
8. Upravo smo se vratili sa *deset* dana putovanja. (We just returned from a ten days trip.)